casebody.data:
Avery LUNDQUIST, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 13-8703. Supreme Court of the United States April 28, 2014.

Case below, 731 F.3d 124.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit. Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and *1941petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit for further consideration in light of Paroline v. United States, 572 U.S. ----, 134 S.Ct. 1710, 188 L.Ed.2d 714 (2014).
